title: New Creator: Greg Narain
body:
Name: Greg Narain

Socials:
https://twitter.com/gregarious
Clubhouse: gregarious

Info:
We believe that questions and answers are the currency of conversation. On social media, the AMA (Ask Me Anything) format dominates. We want to leverage Creator Coin as a means of powering the AMA ecosystem.

Use Cases:
AMAs
Clubhouse consulting
Developing a platform, Zealous, which natively supports use cases as a premium companion toolkit for live creators.

Community Treasury Grant Tier: $1,000

A 'yes' will approve Greg with a $1,000 Community Treasury Gift Coin grant.

A 'no' will deny this proposal.
